---
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Typography Test Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Typography Test Page</h1>
        <p>A comprehensive test page for typography and design elements</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Headings</h2>
            <h1>Heading 1</h1>
            <h2>Heading 2</h2>
            <h3>Heading 3</h3>
            <h4>Heading 4</h4>
            <h5>Heading 5</h5>
            <h6>Heading 6</h6>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Paragraphs</h2>
            <p>This is a standard paragraph. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam dignissim convallis est. Quisque aliquam. Donec faucibus. Nunc iaculis suscipit dui. Nam sit amet sem.</p>
            <p>This is another paragraph with <em>emphasized text</em>, <strong>strong text</strong>, <mark>marked/highlighted text</mark>, <small>small text</small>, <del>deleted text</del>, <ins>inserted text</ins>, <sub>subscript</sub> and <sup>superscript</sup>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Blockquotes</h2>
            <blockquote>
                <p>This is a blockquote. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.</p>
                <cite>— Source Citation</cite>
            </blockquote>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Lists</h2>
            
            <h3>Unordered List</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>List item one</li>
                <li>List item two
                    <ul>
                        <li>Nested list item</li>
                        <li>Another nested list item</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>List item three</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Ordered List</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>List item one</li>
                <li>List item two
                    <ol>
                        <li>Nested list item</li>
                        <li>Another nested list item</li>
                    </ol>
                </li>
                <li>List item three</li>
            </ol>
            
            <h3>Definition List</h3>
            <dl>
                <dt>Definition Term</dt>
                <dd>Definition description. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</dd>
                <dt>Another Definition Term</dt>
                <dd>Another definition description</dd>
            </dl>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Text Alignment</h2>
            <p style="text-align: left;">Left aligned text</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">Center aligned text</p>
            <p style="text-align: right;">Right aligned text</p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;">Justified text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam dignissim convallis est. Quisque aliquam. Donec faucibus. Nunc iaculis suscipit dui. Nam sit amet sem.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Links</h2>
            <p><a href="#">Standard link</a></p>
            <p><a href="#" target="_blank">Link that opens in a new tab</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Code</h2>
            <p>Inline <code>code example</code> within text</p>
          
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Table</h2>
            <table>
                <caption>Sample Table Caption</caption>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Header 1</th>
                        <th>Header 2</th>
                        <th>Header 3</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Row 1, Cell 1</td>
                        <td>Row 1, Cell 2</td>
                        <td>Row 1, Cell 3</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Row 2, Cell 1</td>
                        <td>Row 2, Cell 2</td>
                        <td>Row 2, Cell 3</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Row 3, Cell 1</td>
                        <td>Row 3, Cell 2</td>
                        <td>Row 3, Cell 3</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
                <tfoot>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3">Table footer</td>
                    </tr>
                </tfoot>
            </table>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Forms</h2>
            <form>
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Form Legend</legend>
                    <div>
                        <label for="text-input">Text Input:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="text-input" placeholder="Text input">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="password-input">Password Input:</label>
                        <input type="password" id="password-input" placeholder="Password">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="textarea">Textarea:</label>
                        <textarea id="textarea" rows="4" placeholder="Textarea content"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="select">Select Dropdown:</label>
                        <select id="select">
                            <option value="option1">Option 1</option>
                            <option value="option2">Option 2</option>
                            <option value="option3">Option 3</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label>Checkboxes:</label>
                        <input type="checkbox" id="checkbox1">
                        <label for="checkbox1">Checkbox 1</label>
                        <input type="checkbox" id="checkbox2">
                        <label for="checkbox2">Checkbox 2</label>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label>Radio Buttons:</label>
                        <input type="radio" name="radio-group" id="radio1">
                        <label for="radio1">Radio 1</label>
                        <input type="radio" name="radio-group" id="radio2">
                        <label for="radio2">Radio 2</label>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <button type="button">Standard Button</button>
                        <input type="submit" value="Submit Button">
                        <input type="reset" value="Reset Button">
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Images</h2>
            <figure>
                <img src="/api/placeholder/400/200" alt="Placeholder image">
                <figcaption>Figure caption for the placeholder image</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Horizontal Rule</h2>
            <hr>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Special Characters</h2>
            <p>Copyright © | Registered ® | Trademark ™ | Euro € | Pound £ | Yen ¥ | Ampersand &amp; | Less than &lt; | Greater than &gt;</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Typography Test</h2>
            <p>AaBbCcDdEeFfGgHhIiJjKkLlMmNnOoPpQqRrSsTtUuVvWwXxYyZz</p>
            <p>1234567890!@#$%^&*()_+-=[]{}|;':,./<>?</p>
            <p class="font-serif">Font-serif: AaBbCcDdEeFfGgHhIiJjKkLlMmNnOoPpQqRrSsTtUuVvWwXxYyZz</p>
            <p class="font-mono">Font-mono: AaBbCcDdEeFfGgHhIiJjKkLlMmNnOoPpQqRrSsTtUuVvWwXxYyZz</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Vertical Rhythm</h2>
            <h1>Heading 1</h1>
            <p>Paragraph following heading 1. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam dignissim convallis est.</p>
            <h2>Heading 2</h2>
            <p>Paragraph following heading 2. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam dignissim convallis est.</p>
            <h3>Heading 3</h3>
            <p>Paragraph following heading 3. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam dignissim convallis est.</p>
            <blockquote>
                <p>Blockquote for vertical rhythm testing. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
            </blockquote>
            <p>Paragraph following blockquote. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam dignissim convallis est.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Typography Test Page Footer</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>